sequenceDiagram
    participant Test as Test Script
    participant Appium as Appium Server
    participant App as Mobile App

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over Test,App: STEP 1 -- Type the style command
    Test->>Appium: Find input field (ID: exinput_i)
    Appium->>App: Locate the input field
    Test->>Appium: Type the style command
    Appium->>App: Enter command into input
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
    Note over Test,App: STEP 2 -- Read the result
    Test->>Appium: Find output label (ID: label2_caption)
    Appium->>App: Locate the output label
    Appium-->>Test: Return style value as JSON
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
    Note over Test,App: STEP 3 -- Check the value
    Test->>Test: Parse JSON and get the property
    Test->>Test: Compare with expected token value
    end
